item.description:
Meet at Metro rock at 7:00 PM, then go out for drinks at Tavern on the Square.

Tavern on the Square is at 730 Massachusetts Ave in Cambridge, which is close to the Central T stop on the Red Line. Meet there at 10:30-10:45, we may move on to other locations later. You don't have to climb to join us.

To keep up with us call my cell phone 207-333-8433.

Paul

(Look up MetroRock's web site if you are new to climbing.)
item.how_to_find_us: I'll be at the front table wearing tan shorts, a gray t-shirt and glasses.
item.name: Friday climb then drinks later
